a given day.truefalseis24HrsbooleanrequiredTo denote location is open 24hrs. This can be set to true for type location only.truefalseentitystringrequiredIt can be one value from store, brand or business.storebrandbusinessopensAtstringStore opening time. Required if hours value is not set and isOpen flag is set to true.closesAtstringStore closing time. Required if hours value is not set and isOpen flag is set to true.intervalint32Interval between consecutive store operations hours. Required if hours value is not set and isOpen flag is set to true.hoursarray of objectsArray of Hour If is24Hrs flag is set to false. Required if opensAt, closesAt, interval values are not set.hoursADD  objectResponses 200200Response bodyobjectmessagestring 400400Response bodyobjecterrorsarray of objectserrorsobjecttypestringmessagestringtypestringmessagestringUpdated 8 months ago Delete TimingDelete Timing OverrideLanguageShellNodeRubyPHPPythonCredentialsHeader +1cURL RequestExamplesxxxxxxxxxx141curl --request POST \2     --url https://sandbox.api.deliverysolutions.co/api/v2/timings/location/override \3     --header 'accept: application/json' \4     --header 'content-type: application/json' \5     --header 'tenantId: YOUR_TENANT_ID' \6     --header 'x-api-key: YOUR_API_KEY' \7     --header 'x-compression: true' \8     --data '9{10  "isOpen": true,11  "is24Hrs": true,12  "entity": "store"13}14'Try It!RESPONSEExamplesClick Try It! to start a request and see the response here! Or choose an example:application/json200 - Result400 - If Store Timings are not presentUpdated 8 months ago Delete TimingDelete Timing OverridePlatformIntroductionAuthenticationURLsBusinessCreate BusinesspostBrandsGet Brand DetailsgetCreate BrandpostPackagesDelete PackagedeleteList PackagesgetGet Package DetailsgetUpdate PackagepostCreate PackagepostRatesGet RatespostPickup LocationList LocationsgetGet LocationgetEdit LocationpatchCreate LocationpostBoundaryList BoundariesgetDelete BoundariesdeleteDelete Boundarydelete